videos.description: Rocket Watts' 3-point attempt is off the mark but Luka Garza is there for the offensive rebound and layup.

videos.description: Marcus Bingham Jr. throws up a circus shot that falls and Luka Garza matches him with a layup of his own.

videos.description: Iowa's Luka Garza muscles his way for a layup on Michigan State and coach Tom Izzo is not a happy man.
